      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, dependable runaround, or a solid parts donor? This car isn\u2019t pretending to be perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great for someone handy who wants a cheap set of wheels or a weekend fixer-upper without spending a fortune. Priced to make sense and ready for its next chapter.",
