    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget project with strong enthusiast appeal. This car presents in rough cosmetic shape, but it still offers a fundamentally usable platform with responsive power delivery, a willing drivetrain, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it attractive for someone who prefers turning wrenches over making payments. Starts, runs, and moves, with the character and feedback older analog cars are known for. Not a showpiece, but a straightforward driver/project candidate with real upside for the right owner. Priced to reflect condition while leaving room for improvement.",
